@page
@model PrivacyModel

@{
    // Set the title of the page
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <!-- Main heading for the Privacy Policy -->
            <h1 class="display-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <!-- Introduction and overview of the Privacy Policy -->
            <p class="lead">At Book Catalogue, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the data you provide to us when using our website.</p>

            <!-- Section: Information We Collect -->
            <h2 class="mt-4">Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect personal information, such as your name, email address, and contact details, when you register an account, place an order, or subscribe to our newsletter. We also collect non-personal information, such as your IP address and browsing history, to improve our website's functionality and user experience.</p>

            <!-- Section: Data Security -->
            <h2 class="mt-4">Data Security</h2>
            <p>We take data security seriously and implement industry-standard measures to safeguard your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. We use encryption, firewalls, and other security protocols to protect your data both online and offline.</p>

            <!-- Section: Third-Party Disclosure -->
            <h2 class="mt-4">Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as required by law or to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. We may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in operating our website, conducting business, or servicing you.</p>

            <!-- Section: Updates to This Privacy Policy -->
            <h2 class="mt-4">Updates to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time, and any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

            <!-- Conclusion and contact information -->
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
